# step by step howto

* fdisk /dev/sda
    * g
    * n
    * <enter>
    * <enter>
    * <enter>
* modprobe dm_mod
* fill your partition with random data
    * shred -v /dev/sda
* format drive / initialize your partition
    * cryptsetup --cipher aes-xts-plain64 --key-size 512 --hash sha512 --iter-time 5000 --use-random --verify-passphrase luksFormat /dev/sda
* open partition
    * cryptsetup luksOpen /dev/sda cryptDisk01

